info.brief: Highly technical Marketing Director with experience working on campaigns with over $50,000 per month in adspend. 4 Years of experience and recent MBA from Boise State University. Looking for a position at a high growth startup that help me develop my professional skill set.

highlights: Led a team of 4 people to execute client KPI's.
Managed a marketing budget of over $50,000 a month.
Increased ROI for client XYZ by over 300%.
Created marketing content for Coca Cola for placement on Billboards, Social Media, and Print Advertisement.
Worked in a team of 3 people to execute monthly objectives.
